OL,3,CWitnesses sought after 'threats to
OL,4,Ckill' made on bus
OL,6,FPolice are looking for witnesses after
OL,7,Fa man is alleged to have made 'threats
OL,8,Fto kill' on a Jersey bus.
OL,10,FThe incident took place yesterday
OL,11,Fevening, at approximately 6:40pm, at
OL,12,FLiberation Station in St Helier.
OL,14,FThe suspect allegedly harassed a
OL,15,Ffemale passenger before following her
OL,16,Fonto the 1A bus heading towards Gorey
OL,17,FPier.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
