OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1778335888
OL,3,CWitnesses sought after 'threats to
OL,4,Ckill' made on bus
OL,6,FOn the bus, the suspect allegedly
OL,7,Fcontinued harassing the female
OL,8,Fpassenger. A second male passenger
OL,9,Fthen stepped in which reportedly led
OL,10,Fthe suspect to make threats to kill
OL,11,Fbefore getting off the bus.
OL,13,FThe suspect is said to be a white
OL,14,Fmale, around 40 to 50 years old, bald
OL,15,Fand was wearing an off-white jacket,
OL,16,Fblack trousers and black shoes.
OL,18,FOfficers would like to speak with
OL,19,Fanyone who was at the bus station or
OL,20,Ftravelling on the 1A service at the
OL,21,Ftime and witnessed the incident.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
